race.description: Thank You Rebel Dam Builders Handicap
race.comment: JUST FAMOUS (3) was beaten a whisker twice and then scored easily this grade trip, heavily bet again. Keeps the in-form Fiore and he remains well-placed to go on with the job. PLEASE MIZTER (2) led and won twice over 1400m and a mile before tackling longer and disappointing after an awkward start. Has a handy 3kg claim today and has claims coming back to this trip. COCOON BAY (7) was quickly back on track placing distantly in the JUST FAMOUS race and will run along from the inside gate. Will give a sight. DUBLIN RED (4) turned the form around leading and winning easily at Leonora. Has a low gate and 3kg claim and can't be ruled out back on turf.
